snippet.title: Sunshine Shuffle - ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER (Day of the Devs 2022)
snippet.description:
Sunshine Shuffle is a narrative poker adventure featuring talking animals with criminal pasts and adorable outfits! Play cards with a group of delightful animal friends who robbed the largest bank on the Eastern Seaboard 12 years ago, and are willing to let you decorate their boat in return for not being executed by the mafia.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1912420/
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/StrangeScaffold
DISCORD: https://discordapp.com/invite/YySjWvM
TIKTOK: https://www.tiktok.com/@writnelson
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/WritNelson
